fiveStar.name: Bubble Babies
fiveStar.skill:
Increase healing by 22.0%/22.0%/28.5%/28.5%/35.0%/35.0%/41.5%. Increase multiplier for skill damage from Summer Reminiscence and its healing by 18.5%/24.0%/24.0%/29.5%/29.5%/35.0%/35.0%. When activating Summer Reminiscence, increase the target's damage taken by 8.5%/11.0%/11.0%/13.5%/13.5%/16.0%/16.0% for 3 turns. This effect can stack up to 2 times.
Also decrease the target's Defense and ailment resistance by 12% for 3 turns.
